{"tid":973273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愛滋男健身相中他　偷拍男師如廁！被逮查出一堆鳥照","createTime":"2019-01-08T04:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T05:05:27.000Z","uid":121473,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5140f008d983b26e3afad23ddbe8e3c036ba379c","tid":973273,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T04:25:55.000Z","msg":"公共場合如廁，不僅女性要小心，男性也可能遭偷拍，注意周邊是否有可疑物品。<br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《自由時報》報導，1名28歲男子去年11月在一家百貨公司男廁，涉偷拍1名男子如廁，型男老師赫見1支手機從隔壁間上方空隙伸了進來，嚇得大叫，警方及時到場扣住嫌犯及偷拍的手機。<br />\n<br />\n警方查出，手機另有其他男子上廁所的影像，嫌犯坦承犯案且稱照片未流出，表明自己有同性戀傾向、愛滋病帶原者；被害人發現，嫌犯與自己是同一家健身房會員，但嫌犯稱只是巧合。新竹檢方依妨害秘密罪嫌將阿明提起公訴。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20190108/1496645/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20190108%2F1496645%2F&d=Mpe9G33sanmsJpFg%2BCLz07IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=2ff6a3b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20190108%2F1496645%2F&h=ad8bfe16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20190108/1496645/</a>"},{"pid":"16168895a360ded3e3689d503e2a398ba32eee93","tid":973273,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T04:28:53.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"908b281278163c40c6a12d54eab0fa155bb1fdce","tid":973273,"uid":38131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"愛滋針呀.jpg"},{"pid":"ff68c0041cc13f778b54bfbcff6ca6da630eb7c7","tid":973273,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T04:47:52.000Z","msg":"台灣不意外"},{"pid":"ffc70c80dc3f71a0f4d142f978f56ad5c05687bb","tid":973273,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:05:27.000Z","msg":"推論係0"}]}